hw:
1. PIC (Programmable Interrupt Controller)


regs:
2. Control registers [
	IE : Interrupt Enable,
	IM : Interrupt Mask,
	IP : Interrupt Pending,
	ICC: Instruction Cache Control,
	DCC: Data CC,
	CFG: Config,
	CC : Cycle Counter,
	EBA: Exception Base Address,
	DEBA: Debug EBA,
	JTX, JRX: JTAG Transmit&Receive,
	BP,WP Regs.		
]
3. Zero register (r0)
4. CPU mode change?
